          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The Operations Corridor is narrow and bright in the way only institutional lighting can manage.\n\nFour things compete for your attention: an interlock panel with a calendar sticker, a main lockout point with a small forest of padlocks, a ventilation indicator with a sealed lens, and a stack of procedure placards that look handled often and obeyed rarely.",
